content.rendered:
Directed by Saagar K Chandra

Written by Sachy. Trivikram Srinivas

Star Pawan Kalyan (Bheemla Nayak). Rana Daggubati (Daniel Shekar). Nithya Menen (Suguna). Samyuktha Menon (Daniel’s Wife). Samuthirakani (Jeevan Kumar). Rao Ramesh (Nagaraju). Murli Sharma (Kodanda Ram). Raghu Babu (Balaji).Tanikella Bharani .Teja Kakumanu .Narra Srinivas .Kadambari Kiran . Pammi Sai (Sebastian). Brahmanandam (Judge Anand Rao (Cameo Role)). Sunil (Cameo Appearance (as Suneel)). Sapthagiri (Cameo Appearance). Hyper Aadi (Cameo Appearance)

Language Telugu

Producers Jujjavarapu Mahesh. Harish Pai. Suryadevara Naga Vamsi

Production Sithara Entertainments
